sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>(in-process)
    participant ExtSafety as External Safety Services<br/>(optional, varies)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>(in-process)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails (/v1/chat/completions)
        Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Forwarded headers
        Server->>InputRails: Evaluate input rails
        Note right of InputRails: Content safety check<br/>Jailbreak detection<br/>Injection detection<br/>PII detection<br/>Topic safety

        opt External safety services configured
            InputRails->>ExtSafety: Safety evaluation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (varies)<br/>Auth: API Key
            ExtSafety-->>InputRails: Safety evaluation result
        end

        alt Input rails PASS
            Server->>LLM: Forward chat completion<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            LLM-->>Server: LLM response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
            Server->>OutputRails: Evaluate output rails
            Note right of OutputRails: Hallucination check<br/>Fact checking<br/>Content safety<br/>Topic safety

            opt External safety services configured
                OutputRails->>ExtSafety: Output evaluation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (varies)<br/>Auth: API Key
                ExtSafety-->>OutputRails: Output evaluation result
            end

            alt Output rails PASS
                Server-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)
            else Output rails BLOCK
                Server-->>Client: Blocked response message<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)
            end
        else Input rails BLOCK
            Server-->>Client: Blocked input message<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,ExtSafety: Flow 2: Guardrail-Only Check (/v1/guardrail/checks)
        Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Forwarded headers
        Server->>InputRails: Role-based rail evaluation<br/>(input/output/tool rails)

        opt External safety services configured
            InputRails->>ExtSafety: Rail evaluation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (varies)<br/>Auth: API Key
            ExtSafety-->>InputRails: Rail evaluation result
        end

        Server-->>Client: JSON or NDJSON stream<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)
    end
